      "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "✅ Playwright 1.59 configurado\n✅ 6 browsers: mobile-chromium, -firefox, -webkit + desktop ×3\n✅ trace: retain-on-failure | screenshot: only-on-failure\n✅ home.smoke.spec.ts (seções principais)\n✅ navigation.smoke.spec.ts (drawer, menu)\n✅ portfolio.desktop.smoke.spec.ts (filtros, modal)\n✅ whatsapp.smoke.spec.ts (links, new tab)\n🟡 retries: 2 no CI (fragilidade tolerada)\n🔴 Testes unitários (Jest/Vitest) — ausentes\n🔴 Testes de acessibilidade (axe-core/playwright)\n🔴 Cobertura formal não medida",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "originalText": "✅ Playwright 1.59 configurado\n✅ 6 browsers: mobile-chromium, -firefox, -webkit + desktop ×3\n✅ trace: retain-on-failure | screenshot: only-on-failure\n✅ home.smoke.spec.ts (seções principais)\n✅ navigation.smoke.spec.ts (drawer, menu)\n✅ portfolio.desktop.smoke.spec.ts (filtros, modal)\n✅ whatsapp.smoke.spec.ts (links, new tab)\n🟡 retries: 2 no CI (fragilidade tolerada)\n🔴 Testes unitários (Jest/Vitest) — ausentes\n🔴 Testes de acessibilidade (axe-core/playwright)\n🔴 Cobertura formal não medida",
