      "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "✅ ci.yml: ESLint + tsc --noEmit + prettier + next build\n✅ playwright.yml: smoke/full, manual dispatch com seleção\n✅ azure-static-web-apps-test.yml: build:azure + deploy\n✅ Husky pre-commit: eslint --fix + prettier (lint-staged)\n✅ concurrency: cancel-in-progress em todos os workflows\n✅ paths-filter: dorny/paths-filter@v3 (skip docs-only)\n✅ Build artifacts uploaded (retention: 1 dia)\n✅ Playwright reports uploaded (retention: 7 dias)\n🟡 Branch protection rules — não verificável local\n🟡 Status checks obrigatórios — não confirmados",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "originalText": "✅ ci.yml: ESLint + tsc --noEmit + prettier + next build\n✅ playwright.yml: smoke/full, manual dispatch com seleção\n✅ azure-static-web-apps-test.yml: build:azure + deploy\n✅ Husky pre-commit: eslint --fix + prettier (lint-staged)\n✅ concurrency: cancel-in-progress em todos os workflows\n✅ paths-filter: dorny/paths-filter@v3 (skip docs-only)\n✅ Build artifacts uploaded (retention: 1 dia)\n✅ Playwright reports uploaded (retention: 7 dias)\n🟡 Branch protection rules — não verificável local\n🟡 Status checks obrigatórios — não confirmados",
      "autoResize": true, "lineHeight": 1.5
