    {
      "id": "e056", "type": "text", "x": 664, "y": 1454, "width": 582, "height": 300,
      "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#92400e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null,
      "seed": 56, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 56, "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null, "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false,
      "text": "✅ ESLint: next/core-web-vitals + next/typescript\n✅ Prettier: semi, singleQuote, printWidth=100, tailwind plugin\n✅ TypeScript strict: true (noImplicitAny, strictNullChecks)\n✅ Husky + lint-staged no pre-commit\n✅ reactStrictMode: true (detecta side effects)\n✅ lib/errors/ (ErrorBoundary captura render errors)\n🟡 scripts/performance-check.js (básico, sem CI thresholds)\n🔴 Lighthouse CI — ausente no pipeline\n🔴 Error monitoring (Sentry ou similar) — ausente\n🔴 Bundle size budget — não configurado\n🔴 Web Vitals com envio para backend",
      "fontSize": 12, "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "originalText": "✅ ESLint: next/core-web-vitals + next/typescript\n✅ Prettier: semi, singleQuote, printWidth=100, tailwind plugin\n✅ TypeScript strict: true (noImplicitAny, strictNullChecks)\n✅ Husky + lint-staged no pre-commit\n✅ reactStrictMode: true (detecta side effects)\n✅ lib/errors/ (ErrorBoundary captura render errors)\n🟡 scripts/performance-check.js (básico, sem CI thresholds)\n🔴 Lighthouse CI — ausente no pipeline\n🔴 Error monitoring (Sentry ou similar) — ausente\n🔴 Bundle size budget — não configurado\n🔴 Web Vitals com envio para backend",
